# Honkit build output and dep cache — generated on demand by the
# Pages workflow (.github/workflows/pages.yml). The workflow runs
# Honkit against a staged copy under _stage/book/ rather than this
# directory, so book/ stays pure metadata: only book.json, SUMMARY.md,
# README.md, and this file are committed. If you preview locally by
# copying chapters into book/ directly, you'll see those copies in
# `git status` — clean them up with `git restore book/`.
#
# Don't list chapter filenames here: Honkit reads .gitignore from
# its source dir and silently drops matching files from the build.
_book/
node_modules/
